snippet.title: THE PIONEERS SURVIVING DESOLATION Gameplay Trailer (2022) 4K
snippet.description:
The Pioneers: Surviving Desolation Official Gameplay Trailer New for PC in remastered/upscaled 4K ULTRA HD quality and smooth 60 FPS.

Release date: December 2022

The Pioneers offers a deep and innovative space survival experience. Build your space station, manage your crew and explore the harsh environment of Io, the innermost moon of Jupiter. Are you brave enough to survive? The game is being developed by Supercube.

Enjoy, like & share for more game news videos!
